description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 55, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 165, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20553-65613-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [165 Votes, Top 10% Score]
